data.description: Welcome to your private oasis! This stunning home sits on nearly 2 private, wooded acres. Natural sunlight abounds in this home, and the deck offers the perfect spot for morning coffee and time to slow down. On the main floor, you'll find a spacious kitchen with plenty of room for cooking family meals, multiple living spaces, and a fireplace perfect to curl up in front of in the coming winter. All 3 bedrooms are large and on the second floor. One bedroom includes a private nook perfect for a creative space, or reading lounge. The finished basement offers a massive rec room and the perfect set up for play dates, entertaining, and movie nights! Don't forget the great outdoors! Enjoy autumn walks and hiking on your own property, summertime grilling, and more. This unique property offers the ability to have the best of both worlds - a short commute to schools and the highway, and yet, a private sanctuary waiting for you every day. All kitchen appliances stay. Come meet your new home!
